</p>") (pubDate nil "Wed, 26 May 2010 10:24:18 +0800") (guid ((isPermaLink . "false")) "tag:feed.yeeyan.org:translation/107231") (dc:creator nil "kingsloveqzy") (fs:srclink nil "http://article.yeeyan.org/view/151906/107231") (fs:srcfeed nil "http://www.yeeyan.org/feed/category/410") (fs:itemid nil "feedsky/yeeyan-tech/~8024233/370658297/5032246")))) ("WordPress.com支持短信通知功能" "<p>原作者：<br />来源<a href=\"\">WordPress Adds SMS Notifications, Controls</a><br/>译者<a href=\"http://space.yeeyan.org/u/pestwave\">pestwave</a></p><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-family:arial, helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;font-size:14px;\"><div class=\"asset-body\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;clear:both;font:normal normal normal 14px/0.9em arial, helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5em;\"><p style=\"margin-top:1em;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:1em;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;text-align:left;\"><img src=\"http://rww.readwriteweb.netdna-cdn.com/images/wordpresscom_logo_may09.png\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:10px;padding-bottom:10px;padding-left:10px;border-top-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-left-width:0px;border-style:initial;border-color:initial;border-width:initial;border-color:initial;cursor:auto;float:left;border-style:initial;border-color:initial;\" /></p> <p style=\"margin-top:1em;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:1em;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;text-align:left;\"><a href=\"http://wordpress.com/\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;text-decoration:none;outline-style:none;outline-width:initial;outline-color:initial;color:#cc0000;cursor:pointer;\">WordPress</a>已经开始提供手机短信通知服务了，如果你想通过手机控制你的WordPress.com博客，现在你可以如愿以偿。</p>  <p style=\"margin-top:1em;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:1em;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;text-align:left;\">WordPress推出的新服务包括通知用户博客修改情况、远程批准评论等，只需通过手机编辑短信到“77377”或“PRESS”就可以完成操作。目前仅支持美国手机用户。</p> <p style=\"margin-top:1em;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:1em;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;text-align:left;\"><img src=\"http://rww.readwriteweb.netdna-cdn.com/images/comment_notification-wp.jpg\" alt=\"comment_notification-wp.jpg\" /></p> </div> <div id=\"more\" class=\"asset-more\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;clear:both;font:normal normal normal 14px/0.9em arial, helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5em;\"><p style=\"margin-top:1em;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:1em;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;text-align:left;\">WordPress.com的短信通知服务收费和普通短信一样，包括免费功能和高级付费功能。免费功能包括：通知博主用户增/删情况，博客主题或隐私设置修改情况。付费功能每年20美元，你可以通过含有代码的手机短信保护你的博客，每次登录博客都需要输入这个代码。当你收到新评论时，你可以选择批准、拒绝或回复。</p> <p style=\"margin-top:1em;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:1em;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;text-align:left;\">.<br /> </p> </div> </span><p><a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/pestwave/142519#newComment\">添加新评论</a></p><p><strong>相关文章：</strong></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/153650/142054?from=rss_related\">3招简单将博客转换成电子书</a></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/pestwave/139717?from=rss_related\">iPhone版WordPress支持视频、更好的本地草稿管理</a></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/ecauses/138877?from=rss_related\">非营利组织开展短信活动的五大挑战</a></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/155419/136786?from=rss_related\">[信息视图]短信发送的上升趋势</a></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/106206/137194?from=rss_related\">开车用手机大大增加了交通事故死亡</a></p><img src=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/t1/422809894/yeeyan-tech/feedsky/s.gif?r=http://article.yeeyan.org/view/pestwave/142519\" border=\"0\" height=\"0\" width=\"0\" style=\"position:absolute\" /><p class=\"fswww1\"><a href=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/r/l/feedsky/yeeyan-tech/422809894/art01.html\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" ismap=\"ismap\" src=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/r/i/feedsky/yeeyan-tech/422809894/art01.gif\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\" /></a></p>" "http://article.yeeyan.org/view/pestwave/142519" (19636 7424) old 1 nil nil ((title nil "WordPress.com支持短信通知功能") (link nil "http://article.yeeyan.org/view/pestwave/142519") (created ((xmlns . "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom")) "2010-10-12T08:32:00+00:00") (issued ((xmlns . "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom")) "2010-10-12T08:32:00+00:00") (modified ((xmlns . "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom")) "2010-10-12T08:32:00+00:00") (id ((xmlns . "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom")) "tag:feed.yeeyan.org:translation/142519") (author ((xmlns . "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom")) (name nil "pestwave") (uri nil "http://space.yeeyan.org/u/pestwave")) (content ((xmlns . "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom") (type . "html")) "<p>原作者：<br />来源<a href=\"\">WordPress Adds SMS Notifications, Controls</a><br/>译者<a href=\"http://space.yeeyan.org/u/pestwave\">pestwave</a></p><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-family:arial, helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;font-size:14px;\"><div class=\"asset-body\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;clear:both;font:normal normal normal 14px/0.9em arial, helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5em;\"><p style=\"margin-top:1em;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:1em;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;text-align:left;\"><img src=\"http://rww.readwriteweb.netdna-cdn.com/images/wordpresscom_logo_may09.png\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:10px;padding-bottom:10px;padding-left:10px;border-top-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-left-width:0px;border-style:initial;border-color:initial;border-width:initial;border-color:initial;cursor:auto;float:left;border-style:initial;border-color:initial;\" /></p> <p style=\"margin-top:1em;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:1em;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;text-align:left;\"><a href=\"http://wordpress.com/\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;text-decoration:none;outline-style:none;outline-width:initial;outline-color:initial;color:#cc0000;cursor:pointer;\">WordPress</a>已经开始提供手机短信通知服务了，如果你想通过手机控制你的WordPress.com博客，现在你可以如愿以偿。</p>  <p style=\"margin-top:1em;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:1em;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;text-align:left;\">WordPress推出的新服务包括通知用户博客修改情况、远程批准评论等，只需通过手机编辑短信到“77377”或“PRESS”就可以完成操作。目前仅支持美国手机用户。</p> <p style=\"margin-top:1em;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:1em;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;text-align:left;\"><img src=\"http://rww.readwriteweb.netdna-cdn.com/images/comment_notification-wp.jpg\" alt=\"comment_notification-wp.jpg\" /></p> </div> <div id=\"more\" class=\"asset-more\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;clear:both;font:normal normal normal 14px/0.9em arial, helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5em;\"><p style=\"margin-top:1em;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:1em;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;text-align:left;\">WordPress.com的短信通知服务收费和普通短信一样，包括免费功能和高级付费功能。免费功能包括：通知博主用户增/删情况，博客主题或隐私设置修改情况。付费功能每年20美元，你可以通过含有代码的手机短信保护你的博客，每次登录博客都需要输入这个代码。当你收到新评论时，你可以选择批准、拒绝或回复。</p> <p style=\"margin-top:1em;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:1em;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;text-align:left;\">.<br /> </p> </div> </span><p><a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/pestwave/142519#newComment\">添加新评论</a></p><p><strong>相关文章：</strong></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/153650/142054?from=rss_related\">3招简单将博客转换成电子书</a></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/pestwave/139717?from=rss_related\">iPhone版WordPress支持视频、更好的本地草稿管理</a></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/ecauses/138877?from=rss_related\">非营利组织开展短信活动的五大挑战</a></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/155419/136786?from=rss_related\">[信息视图]短信发送的上升趋势</a></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/106206/137194?from=rss_related\">开车用手机大大增加了交通事故死亡</a></p>") (content:encoded nil "<p>原作者：<br />来源<a href=\"\">WordPress Adds SMS Notifications, Controls</a><br/>译者<a href=\"http://space.yeeyan.org/u/pestwave\">pestwave</a></p><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-family:arial, helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;font-size:14px;\"><div class=\"asset-body\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;clear:both;font:normal normal normal 14px/0.9em arial, helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5em;\"><p style=\"margin-top:1em;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:1em;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;text-align:left;\"><img src=\"http://rww.readwriteweb.netdna-cdn.com/images/wordpresscom_logo_may09.png\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:10px;padding-bottom:10px;padding-left:10px;bor