eneral.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Apple car\" /> </p> &nbsp;&nbsp;<blockquote>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;How would look like a car invented and designed by Apple? Italy based auto designer<span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><blockquote style=\"display:inline !important;\"><a onclick=\"javascript:pageTracker._trackPageview('/outgoing/liviutudoran.blogspot.com/');\" href=\"http://liviutudoran.blogspot.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Liviu Tudoran</a></blockquote> </span>has taken inspiration from the Apple Macintosh products and designed a concept car called iMove for the year 2020. This car will be electric, of course, and will feature the same general design lines like all the latest Macintosh products. Most of the car body is covered with transparent materials, so that even under the roof the driver get a cabriolet feeling. This transparent material is also a solar panel. iMove will be able to seat three passengers and will feature an innovative luggage storage space. The concept will also offer various possibilities for customization, so the owners will be able to change the car’s appliance according to its own preferences.</blockquote> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;如果苹果要创造设计汽车，最后看起来会是怎么样的呢？意大利汽车设计师Liviu Tudoran已从苹果Macintosh产品的灵感设计出了2020年的名为iMove的概念车。这将是一辆电动车，当然的，将具有所有最新Macintosh产品一样的设计风格。大部分的车身覆盖着透明材料，使即使在盖上车顶，司机也会得到敞篷车的感觉。这种透明材料同时也是太阳能电池板。 iMove将可以乘坐三名乘客，并配备有创新的行李储存空间。这概念车也将提供定制带来的各种可能性，因此，车主可以根据自己的喜好改变车的外观。 </p> <p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p> <p>&nbsp;&nbsp; <img src=\"http://www.beautifullife.info/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/11/01.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Apple car\" /> </p> <p>&nbsp;&nbsp; <img src=\"http://www.beautifullife.info/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/11/02.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Apple car\" /> </p> <p>&nbsp;&nbsp; <img src=\"http://www.beautifullife.info/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/11/03.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Apple car\" /> </p> <p>&nb