7/140524?from=rss_related\">碟型气球可以将整栋建筑运送到遥远的地方</a></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/126492/94503?from=rss_related\">船用备件如何得到处理</a></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/pestwave/49274?from=rss_related\">运输应用：我们到位了吗？</a></p><img src=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/t1/422733116/yeeyan-tech/feedsky/s.gif?r=http://article.yeeyan.org/view/76253/142417\" border=\"0\" height=\"0\" width=\"0\" style=\"position:absolute\" /><p class=\"fswww1\"><a href=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/r/l/feedsky/yeeyan-tech/422733116/art01.html\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" ismap=\"ismap\" src=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/r/i/feedsky/yeeyan-tech/422733116/art01.gif\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\" /></a></p>") (pubDate nil "Tue, 12 Oct 2010 10:24:50 +0800") (guid ((isPermaLink . "false")) "tag:feed.yeeyan.org:translation/142417") (dc:creator nil "colachoco") (fs:srclink nil "http://article.yeeyan.org/view/76253/142417") (fs:srcfeed nil "http://www.yeeyan.org/feed/category/410") (fs:itemid nil "feedsky/yeeyan-tech/~8024233/422733116/5032246"))) ("触摸屏革命性新技术——给你不同材质的触感" "<p>原作者：<br />来源<a href=\"http://www.techi.com/2010/10/new-tech-could-create-textured-touch-screens/\">New Tech Could Create Textured Touch Screens | Techicom</a><br/>译者<a href=\"http://space.yeeyan.org/u/175252\">吴二</a></p><p><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2010-10/12/20101012101017_93915.gif\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></p> <p><p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.5pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:15.0pt;\"><span style=\"color:#292929;font-size:16px;\">（指尖活动，绝缘层</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;font-size:16px;\">/</span><span style=\"color:#292929;font-size:16px;\">透明电极</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;font-size:16px;\">/</span><span style=\"color:#292929;font-size:16px;\">玻璃板）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;\"><o</o</span></p> <p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.5pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:15.0pt;\"><span style=\"color:#292929;font-size:16px;\"><br /> </span></p> <font class=\"Apple-style-span\" color=\"#292929\" size=\"6\"><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-size:19px;line-height:20px;\"><p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.5pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;\">我们都知道触摸屏存在的问题。开会的时候，你无法在桌子下面打字。开车的时候也没有办法打字。只要你在同时做其它事，没有专心盯着屏幕来确定你点击到了正确的字母，就没有办法输入文字。</span></p> <p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.5pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;\">现在诞生了一种新技术，能够使触摸屏提供一个触摸反馈，让平滑的玻璃板也能拥有其它材质的手感。</span></p> <p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.5pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;\">卡耐基</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;\">-</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;\">梅隆大学的博士生克里斯</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;\">-</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;\">哈里逊希望能改变这种现状。他正在同迪士尼研究中心合作研发这种新技术，并首次将它命名为“</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;\">TeslaTouch</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;\">”。</span></p> <p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.5pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;\">他们的创意是当手指滑过屏幕的时候，会有微小的电流产生信号声或振动感。</span></p> <p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.5pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;\">调节到不同的频率或是交替使用，产生反馈的程度也不同，还有不同的触摸质感可供选择。</span></p> <p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.5pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;\">这项技术的潜力是显而易见的。当拖动一张图片或是其它文件的时候，不同类型的文件会有不同的触感。拉伸图片还会有伸缩弹性的感觉。</span></p> <p style=\"line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\"Timesnewroman\";mso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\"\">据悉，这项巨大的技术突破将首先应用在那些喜欢开车时打字的人身上，实在令人悲伤。</span></p> <br /> <br /> </span></font></p><p><a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/175252/142419#newComment\">添加新评论</a></p><p><strong>相关文章：</strong></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/160937/141025?from=rss_related\">美国《财富》杂志网站--猿力亦不可破的玻璃   解密触摸屏背后的科技</a></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/155419/123663?from=rss_related\">未来显示器：3D触摸屏</a></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/keanohan/108732?from=rss_related\">海豚利用iPad触摸屏与人类交流</a></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/remex/108743?from=rss_related\">《大众科学》：海豚利用iPad与人交流</a></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/148906/105582?from=rss_related\">现在，手机的数据接收功能的使用比通话功能要多了——纽约时报网</a></p><img src=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/t1/422677565/yeeyan-tech/feedsky/s.gif?r=http://article.yeeyan.org/view/175252/142419\" border=\"0\" height=\"0\" width=\"0\" style=\"position:absolute\" /><p class=\"fswww1\"><a href=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/r/l/feedsky/yeeyan-tech/422677565/art01.html\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" ismap=\"ismap\" src=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/r/i/feedsky/yeeyan-tech/422677565/art01.gif\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\" /></a></p>" "http://article.yeeyan.org/view/175252/142419" (19635 49972) old 9 nil nil ((title nil "触摸屏革命性新技术——给你不同材质的触感") (link nil "http://article.yeeyan.org/view/175252/142419") (created ((xmlns . "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom")) "2010-10-12T02:08:52+00:00") (issued ((xmlns . "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom")) "2010-10-12T02:08:52+00:00") (modified ((xmlns . "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom")) "2010-10-12T02:08:52+00:00") (id ((xmlns . "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom")) "tag:feed.yeeyan.org:translation/142419") (author ((xmlns . "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom")) (name nil "吴二") (uri nil "http://space.yeeyan.org/u/175252")) (content ((xmlns . "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom") (type . "html")) "<p>原作者：<br />来源<a href=\"http://www.techi.com/2010/10/new-tech-could-create-textured-touch-screens/\">New Tech Could Create Textured Touch Screens | Techicom</a><br/>译者<a href=\"http://space.yeeyan.org/u/175252\">吴二</a></p><p><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2010-10/12/20101012101017_93915.gif\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></p> <p><p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.5pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:15.0pt;\"><span style=\"color:#292929;font-size:16px;\">（指尖活动，绝缘层</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;font-size:16px;\">/</span><span style=\"color:#292929;font-size:16px;\">透明电极</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;font-size:16px;\">/</span><span style=\"color:#292929;font-size:16px;\">玻璃板）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;\"><o</o</span></p> <p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.5pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:15.0pt;\"><span style=\"color:#292929;font-size:16px;\"><br /> </span></p> <font class=\"Apple-style-span\" color=\"#292929\" size=\"6\"><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-size:19px;line-height:20px;\"><p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.5pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;\">我们都知道触摸屏存在的问题。开会的时候，你无法在桌子下面打字。开车的时候也没有办法打字。只要你在同时做其它事，没有专心盯着屏幕来确定你点击到了正确的字母，就没有办法输入文字。</span></p> <p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.5pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;\">现在诞生了一种新技术，能够使触摸屏提供一个触摸反馈，让平滑的玻璃板也能拥有其它材质的手感。</span></p> <p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.5pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;\">卡耐基</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;\">-</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;\">梅隆大学的博士生克里斯</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;\">-</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;\">哈里逊希望能改变这种现状。他正在同迪士尼研究中心合作研发这种新技术，并首次将它命名为“</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;\">TeslaTouch</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;\">”。</span></p> <p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.5pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;\">他们的创意是当手指滑过屏幕的时候，会有微小的电流产生信号声或振动感。</span></p> <p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.5pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;\">调节到不同的频率或是交替使用，产生反馈的程度也不同，还有不同的触摸质感可供选择。</span></p> <p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.5pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;\">这项技术的潜力是显而易见的。当拖动一张图片或是其它文件的时候，不同类型的文件会有不同的触感。拉伸图片还会有伸缩弹性的感觉。</span></p> <p style=\"line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\"Timesnewroman\";mso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\"\">据悉，这项巨大的技术突破将首先应用在那些喜欢开车时打字的人身上，实在令人悲伤。</span></p> <br /> <br /> </span></font></p><p><a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/175252/142419#newComment\">添加新评论</a></p><p><strong>相关文章：</strong></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/160937/141025?from=rss_related\">美国《财富》杂志网站--猿力亦不可破的玻璃   解密触摸屏背后的科技</a></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/155419/123663?from=rss_related\">未来显示器：3D触摸屏</a></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/keanohan/108732?from=rss_related\">海豚利用iPad触摸屏与人类交流</a></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/remex/108743?from=rss_related\">《大众科学》：海豚利用iPad与人交流</a></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/148906/105582?from=rss_related\">现在，手机的数据接收功能的使用比通话功能要多了——纽约时报网</a></p>") (content:encoded nil "<p>原作者：<br />来源<a href=\"http://www.techi.com/2010/10/new-tech-could-create-textured-touch-screens/\">New Tech Could Create Textured Touch Screens | Techicom</a><br/>译者<a href=\"http://space.yeeyan.org/u/175252\">吴二</a></p><p><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2010-10/12/20101012101017_93915.gif\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></p> <p><p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.5pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:15.0pt;\"><span style=\"color:#292929;font-size:16px;\">（指尖活动，绝缘层</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;font-size:16px;\">/</span><span style=\"color:#292929;font-size:16px;\">透明电极</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;font-size:16px;\">/</span><span style=\"color:#292929;font-size:16px;\">玻璃板）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;\"><o</o</span></p> <p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.5pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:15.0pt;\"><span style=\"color:#292929;font-size:16px;\"><br /> </span></p> <font class=\"Apple-style-span\" color=\"#292929\" size=\"6\"><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-size:19px;line-height:20px;\"><p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.5pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;\">我们都知道触摸屏存在的问题。开会的时候，你无法在桌子下面打字。开车的时候也没有办法打字。只要你在同时做其它事，没有专心盯着屏幕来确定你点击到了正确的字母，就没有办法输入文字。</span></p> <p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.5pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;\">现在诞生了一种新技术，能够使触摸屏提供一个触摸反馈，让平滑的玻璃板也能拥有其它材质的手感。</span></p> <p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.5pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;\">卡耐基</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;\">-</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;\">梅隆大学的博士生克里斯</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;\">-</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;\">哈里逊希望能改变这种现状。他正在同迪士尼研究中心合作研发这种新技术，并首次将它命名为“</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;\">TeslaTouch</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;\">”。</span></p> <p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.5pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;\">他们的创意是当手指滑过屏幕的时候，会有微小的电流产生信号声或振动感。</span></p> <p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.5pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;\">调节到不同的频率或是交替使用，产生反馈的程度也不同，还有不同的触摸质感可供选择。</span></p> <p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.5pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;color:#292929;\">这项技术的潜力是显而易见的。当拖动一张图片或是其它文件的时候，不同类型的文件会有不同的触感。拉伸图片还会有伸缩弹性的感觉。</span></p> <p style=\"line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\"Timesnewroman\";mso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\"\">据悉，这项巨大的技术突破将首先应用在那些喜欢开车时打字的人身上，实在令人悲伤。</span></p> <br /> <br /> </span></font></p><p><a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/175252/142419#newComment\">添加新评论</a></p><p><strong>相关文章：</strong></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/160937/141025?from=rss_related\">美国《财富》杂志网站--猿力亦不可破的玻璃   解密触摸屏背后的科技</a></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/155419/123663?from=rss_related\">未来显示器：3D触摸屏</a></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/keanohan/108732?from=rss_related\">海豚利用iPad触摸屏与人类交流</a></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/remex/108743?from=rss_related\">《大众科学》：海豚利用iPad与人交流</a></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/148906/105582?from=rss_related\">现在，手机的数据接收功能的使用比通话功能要多了——纽约时报网</a></p><img src=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/t1/422677565/yeeyan-tech/feedsky/s.gif?r=http://article.yeeyan.org/view/175252/142419\" border=\"0\" height=\"0\" width=\"0\" style=\"position:absolute\" /><p class=\"fswww1\"><a href=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/r/l/feedsky/yeeyan-tech/422677565/art01.html\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" ismap=\"ismap\" src=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/r/i/feedsky/yeeyan-tech/422677565/art01.gif\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\" /></a></p>") (pubDate nil "Tue, 12 Oct 2010 10:08:52 +0800") (guid ((isPermaLink . "false")) "tag:feed.yeeyan.org:translation/142419") (dc:creator nil "吴二") (fs:srclink nil "http://article.yeeyan.org/view/175252/142419") (fs:srcfeed nil "http://www.yeeyan.org/feed/category/410") (fs:itemid nil "feedsky/yeeyan-tech/~8024233/422677565/5032246"))) ("商业航天飞机进行了第一次自由飞行试验" "<p>原作者：<br />来源<a href=\"http://news.discovery.com/space/commercial-spaceship-flies-free-in-first-glide-test.html\">【Discovery News】Commercial Spaceship Flies Free In First Glide Test</a><br/>译者<a href=\"http://space.yeeyan.org/u/176599\">丰子余</a></p><blockquote>Virgin Galactic's commercial suborbital spaceship completed its first free flight on Sunday, gliding from an altitude of 45,000 feet to a landing at the Mojave Air Space Port in California.</blockquote> <p>Virgin Galactic的商业宇宙飞船在周日进行了它的第一次自由飞行，从45000英尺的高度向下滑翔，在加利福尼亚的莫哈韦航空航天港最终降落。</p> <blockquote>The spaceship, named VSS Enterprise, has made four previous forays into the air attached beneath a carrier aircraft known as WhiteKnightTwo. Sunday's test flight was the spaceship's first solo.</blockquote> <p>名为VSS Enterprise的宇宙飞船曾附在WhiteKnightTwo号般载飞机上作过四次空中飞行。周日的试验飞行是它得处女单独航行。</p> <blockquote>\"This was one of the most exciting days in the whole history of Virgin,\" company founder and chief executive Richard Branson said in a statement. </blockquote> <p>“这是Virgin有史以来最激动人心的一天之一，”公司创立者与董事长理查德·布兰森在一份声明中说道。</p> <blockquote>\"For the first time since we seriously began the project in 2004, I watched the world’s first manned commercial spaceship landing on the runway at Mojave Air and Space Port and it was a great moment.\" </blockquote> <p>“自从我们在2004年认真地启动这个计划的时候，我第一次看到了世界上首次有人国足驾驶的商业飞船降落在莫哈韦航空航天港，那是一个伟大的时刻。”</p> <blockquote>Sunday's flight clears spaceship builder Scaled Composites to begin rocket-powered flights next year, and test flights in space in late 2011 or early 2012.</blockquote> <p>周日的飞行明确了宇宙飞船建造商Scaled Composites 将要在明年开启装有火箭发动机的飞行计划，在太空中的试验飞行将在2011年底或2012年初进行。</p> <blockquote>Virgin Galactic, which is selling rides on the spaceship for $200,000, has collected $50 million in deposits from 370 customers so far. If all goes well, passenger service could begin by the end of 2011.</blockquote> <p>Virgin Galactic公司对宇宙飞船的每个座位定价是200000美元，现在它已经从370位顾客中收到了5千万美元。如果一切进行顺利的话，乘客会在2011年底升上太空。</p> <blockquote>VSS Enterprise is a six-passenger, two-pilot ship closely modeled on Scaled's prototype vehicle, SpaceShipOne, which won the $10 million Ansari X Prize competition in 2004 for the first -- and so far only -- privately funded, piloted spaceflights.</blockquote> <p>VSS Enterprise 是一个有两名飞行员，可载6名乘客的飞船，完全模仿Scaled的原型机SpaceShipOne。SpaceShipOne曾经在2004年赢得一千万Ansari X 奖金，它进行了迄今为止第一次也是惟一一次个人建造的飞船带飞行员的太空飞行。</p> <blockquote>\"The VSS Enterprise was a real joy to fly, especially when one considers the fact that the vehicle has been designed not only to be a Mach 3.5 spaceship capable of going into space but also one of the world's highest altitude gliders,\" Pete Siebold, who piloted the ship during Sunday's test flight, said in a statement.</blockquote> <p>“VSS Enterprise公司对此次飞行非常开心，尤其是当人们认识到它不仅仅是被设计成一个3.5马赫的能够飞到太空中的航天飞机而且是世界上飞行高度最高的滑翔机之一的事实的时候，”Pete Siebold（周日试验飞行的指导者）在一份声明中谈道。</p> <blockquote>\"Our challenge going forward will be to complete our experimental program, obtain our FAA licence and safely bring the system into service at Spaceport America, New Mexico,\" added Virgin Galactic CEO George Whitesides.</blockquote> <p>“我们接下来的挑战是完成我们的试验计划，然后获得FAA执照，同时安全地将我们的计划正式到新墨西哥美国宇航中心转化成服务。”Virgin Galactic CEO George Whitesides补充道。</p><p><a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/176599/142273#newComment\">添加新评论</a></p><p><strong>相关文章：</strong></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/104014/142348?from=rss_related\">欧股走高，美国股指期货上扬，外界猜测美联储提振经济</a></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/104014/142353?from=rss_related\">美股开盘小幅走高，预计美联储出台措施</a></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/119249/142186?from=rss_related\">中国的亿万富翁愿意分享他们的财富吗？</a></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/134956/142214?from=rss_related\">中国的亿万富翁们能分享财富吗？</a></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/104014/142247?from=rss_related\">欧股开盘小幅走高，易捷航空涨幅居前</a></p><img src=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/t1/422636670/yeeyan-tech/feedsky/s.gif?r=http://article.yeeyan.org/view/176599/142273\" border=\"0\" height=\"0\" width=\"0\" style=\"position:absolute\" /><p class=\"fswww1\"><a href=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/r/l/feedsky/yeeyan-tech/422636670/art01.html\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" ismap=\"ismap\" src=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/r/i/feedsky/yeeyan-tech/422636670/art01.gif\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\" /></a></p>" "http://article.yeeyan.org/view/176599/142273" (19635 45609) old 10 nil nil ((title nil "商业航天飞机进行了第一次自由飞行试验") (link nil "http://article.yeeyan.org/view/176599/142273") (created ((xmlns . "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom")) "2010-10-12T00:56:09+00:00") (issued ((xmlns . "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom")) "2010-10-12T00:56:09+00:00") (modified ((xmlns . "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom")) "2010-10-12T00:56:09+00:00") (id ((xmlns . "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom")) "tag:feed.yeeyan.org:translation/142273") (author ((xmlns . "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom")) (name nil "丰子余") (uri nil "http://space.yeeyan.org/u/176599")) (content ((xmlns . "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom") (type . "html")) "<p>原作者：<br />来源<a href=\"http://news.discovery.com/space/commercial-spaceship-flies-free-in-first-glide-test.html\">【Discovery News】Commercial Spaceship Flies Free In First Glide Test</a><br/>译者<a href=\"http://space.yeeyan.org/u/176599\">丰子余</a></p><blockquote>Virgin Galactic's commercial suborbital spaceship completed its first free flight on Sunday, gliding from an altitude of 45,000 feet to a landing at the Mojave Air Space Port in California.</blockquote> <p>Virgin Galactic的商业宇宙飞船在周日进行了它的第一次自由飞行，从45000英尺的高度向下滑翔，在加利福尼亚的莫哈韦航空航天港最终降落。</p> <blockquote>The spaceship, named VSS Enterprise, has made four previous forays into the air attached beneath a carrier aircraft known as WhiteKnightTwo. Sunday's test flight was the spaceship's first solo.</blockquote> <p>名为VSS Enterprise的宇宙飞船曾附在WhiteKnightTwo号般载飞机上作过四次空中飞行。周日的试验飞行是它得处女单独航行。</p> <blockquote>\"This was one of the most exciting days in the whole history of Virgin,\" company founder and chief executive Richard Branson said in a statement. </blockquote> <p>“这是Virgin有史以来最激动人心的一天之一，”公司创立者与董事长理查德·布兰森在一份声明中说道。</p> <blockquote>\"For the first time since we seriously began the project in 2004, I watched the world’s first manned commercial spaceship landing on the runway at Mojave Air and Space Port and it was a great moment.\" </blockquote> <p>“自从我们在2004年认真地启动这个计划的时候，我第一次看到了世界上首次有人国足驾驶的商业飞船降落在莫哈韦航空航天港，那是一个伟大的时刻。”</p> <blockquote>Sunday's flight clears spaceship builder Scaled Composites to begin rocket-powered flights next year, and test flights in space in late 2011 or early 2012.</blockquote> <p>周日的飞行明确了宇宙飞船建造商Scaled Composites 将要在明年开启装有火箭发动机的飞行计划，在太空中的试验飞行将在2011年底或2012年初进行。</p> <blockquote>Virgin Galactic, which is selling rides on the spaceship for $200,000, has collected $50 million in deposits from 370 customers so far. If all goes well, passenger service could begin by the end of 2011.</blockquote> <p>Virgin Galactic公司对宇宙飞船的每个座位定价是200000美元，现在它已经从370位顾客中收到了5千万美元。如果一切进行顺利的话，乘客会在2011年底升上太空。</p> <blockquote>VSS Enterprise is a six-passenger, two-pilot ship closely modeled on Scaled's prototype vehicle, SpaceShipOne, which won the $10 million Ansari X Prize competition in 2004 for the first -- and so far only -- privately funded, piloted spaceflights.</blockquote> <p>VSS Enterprise 是一个有两名飞行员，可载6名乘客的飞船，完全模仿Scaled的原型机SpaceShipOne。SpaceShipOne曾经在2004年赢得一千万Ansari X 奖金，它进行了迄今为止第一次也是惟一一次个人建造的飞船带飞行员的太空飞行。</p> <blockquote>\"The VSS Enterprise was a real joy to fly, especially when one considers the fact that the vehicle has been designed not only to be a Mach 3.5 spaceship capable of going into space but also one of the world's highest altitude gliders,\" Pete Siebold, who piloted the ship during Sunday's test flight, said in a statement.</blockquote> <p>“VSS Enterprise公司对此次飞行非常开心，尤其是当人们认识到它不仅仅是被设计成一个3.5马赫的能够飞到太空中的航天飞机而且是世界上飞行高度最高的滑翔机之一的事实的时候，”Pete Siebold（周日试验飞行的指导者）在一份声明中谈道。</p> <blockquote>\"Our challenge going forward will be to complete our experimental program, obtain our FAA licence and safely bring the system into service at Spaceport America, New Mexico,\" added Virgin Galactic CEO George Whitesides.</blockquote> <p>“我们接下来的挑战是完成我们的试验计划，然后获得FAA执照，同时安全地将我们的计划正式到新墨西哥美国宇航中心转化成服务。”Virgin Galactic CEO George Whitesides补充道。</p><p><a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/176599/142273#newComment\">添加新评论</a></p><p><strong>相关文章：</strong></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/104014/142348?from=rss_related\">欧股走高，美国股指期货上扬，外界猜测美联储提振经济</a></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/104014/142353?from=rss_related\">美股开盘小幅走高，预计美联储出台措施</a></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/119249/142186?from=rss_related\">中国的亿万富翁愿意分享他们的财富吗？</a></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/134956/142214?from=rss_related\">中国的亿万富翁们能分享财富吗？</a></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/104014/142247?from=rss_related\">欧股开盘小幅走高，易捷航空涨幅居前</a></p>") (content:encoded nil "<p>原作者：<br />来源<a href=\"http://news.discovery.com/space/commercial-spaceship-flies-free-in-first-glide-test.html\">【Discovery News】Commercial Spaceship Flies Free In First Glide Test</a><br/>译者<a href=\"http://space.yeeyan.org/u/176599\">丰子余</a></p><blockquote>Virgin Galactic's commercial suborbital spaceship completed its first free flight on Sunday, gliding from an altitude of 45,000 feet to a landing at the Mojave Air Space Port in California.</blockquote> <p>Virgin Galactic的商业宇宙飞船在周日进行了它的第一次自由飞行，从45000英尺的高度向下滑翔，在加利福尼亚的莫哈韦航空航天港最终降落。</p> <blockquote>The spaceship, named VSS Enterprise, has made four previous forays into the air attached beneath a carrier aircraft known as WhiteKnightTwo. Sunday's test flight was the spaceship's first solo.</blockquote> <p>名为VSS Enterprise的宇宙飞船曾附在WhiteKnightTwo号般载飞机上作过四次空中飞行。周日的试验飞行是它得处女单独航行。</p> <blockquote>\"This was one of the most exciting days in the whole history of Virgin,\" company founder and chief executive Richard Branson said in a statement. </blockquote> <p>“这是Virgin有史以来最激动人心的一天之一，”公司创立者与董事长理查德·布兰森在一份声明中说道。</p> <blockquote>\"For the first time since we seriously began the project in 2004, I watched the world’s first manned commercial spaceship landing on the runway at Mojave Air and Space Port and it was a great moment.\" </blockquote> <p>“自从我们在2004年认真地启动这个计划的时候，我第一次看到了世界上首次有人国足驾驶的商业飞船降落在莫哈韦航空航天港，那是一个伟大的时刻。”</p> <blockquote>Sunday's flight clears spaceship builder Scaled Composites to begin rocket-powered flights next year, and test flights in space in late 2011 or early 2012.</blockquote> <p>周日的飞行明确了宇宙飞船建造商Scaled Composites 将要在明年开启装有火箭发动机的飞行计划，在太空中的试验飞行将在2011年底或2012年初进行。</p> <blockquote>Virgin Galactic, which is selling rides on the spaceship for $200,000, has collected $50 million in deposits from 370 customers so far. If all goes well, passenger service could begin by the end of 2011.</blockquote> <p>Virgin Galactic公司对宇宙飞船的每个座位定价是200000美元，现在它已经从370位顾客中收到了5千万美元。如果一切进行顺利的话，乘客会在2011年底升上太空。</p> <blockquote>VSS Enterprise is a six-passenger, two-pilot ship closely modeled on Scaled's prototype vehicle, SpaceShipOne, which won the $10 million Ansari X Prize competition in 2004 for the first -- and so far only -- privately funded, piloted spaceflights.</blockquote> <p>VSS Enterprise 是一个有两名飞行员，可载6名乘客的飞船，完全模仿Scaled的原型机SpaceShipOne。SpaceShipOne曾经在2004年赢得一千万Ansari X 奖金，它进行了迄今为止第一次也是惟一一次个人建造的飞船带飞行员的太空飞行。</p> <blockquote>\"The VSS Enterprise was a real joy to fly, especially when one considers the fact that the vehicle has been designed not only to be a Mach 3.5 spaceship capable of going into space but also one of the world's highest altitude gliders,\" Pete Siebold, who piloted the ship during Sunday's test flight, said in a statement.</blockquote> <p>“VSS Enterprise公司对此次飞行非常开心，尤其是当人们认识到它不仅仅是被设计成一个3.5马赫的能够飞到太空中的航天飞机而且是世界上飞行高度最高的滑翔机之一的事实的时候，”Pete Siebold（周日试验飞行的指导者）在一份声明中谈道。</p> <blockquote>\"Our challenge going forward will be to complete our experimental program, obtain our FAA licence and safely bring the system into service at Spaceport America, New Mexico,\" added Virgin Galactic CEO George Whitesides.</blockquote> <p>“我们接下来的挑战是完成我们的试验计划，然后获得FAA执照，同时安全地将我们的计划正式到新墨西哥美国宇航中心转化成服务。”Virgin Galactic CEO George Whitesides补充道。</p><p><a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/176599/142273#newComment\">添加新评论</a></p><p><strong>相关文章：</strong></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/104014/142348?from=rss_related\">欧股走高，美国股指期货上扬，外界猜测美联储提振经济</a></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/104014/142353?from=rss_related\">美股开盘小幅走高，预计美联储出台措施</a></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/119249/142186?from=rss_related\">中国的亿万富翁愿意分享他们的财富吗？</a></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/134956/142214?from=rss_related\">中国的亿万富翁们能分享财富吗？</a></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/104014/142247?from=rss_related\">欧股开盘小幅走高，易捷航空涨幅居前</a></p><img src=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/t1/422636670/yeeyan-tech/feedsky/s.gif?r=http://article.yeeyan.org/view/176599/142273\" border=\"0\" height=\"0\" width=\"0\" style=\"position:absolute\" /><p class=\"fswww1\"><a href=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/r/l/feedsky/yeeyan-tech/422636670/art01.html\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" ismap=\"ismap\" src=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/r/i/feedsky/yeeyan-tech/422636670/art01.gif\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\" /></a></p>") (pubDate nil "Tue, 12 Oct 2010 08:56:09 +0800") (guid ((isPermaLink . "false")) "tag:feed.yeeyan.org:translation/142273") (dc:creator nil "丰子余") (fs:srclink nil "http://article.yeeyan.org/view/176599/142273") (fs:srcfeed nil "http://www.yeeyan.org/feed/category/410") (fs:itemid nil "feedsky/yeeyan-tech/~8024233/422636670/5032246"))))